{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overall:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tu Tien Path is a 3D Xianxia Cultivation game, Fantasy Adventure RPG in UNREAL ENGINE 5.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are free on your own path in the world. But you will be loneliness, and very consistency if you want to go to the highest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It\u2019s a part of a web novel, Q-Style with stylized object model and colors world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In mortal world, there are 5 levels in the Xianxia Cultivation Path that a normal human can achieve, of course you must spend blood and bone for it. Consistency and effort are not enough, luck will play a big part in it.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Third-Person \u2013 Adventure RPG \u2013 Action \u2013 Shooting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Open world \u2013 Flight - Stealth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crafting \u2013 Building \u2013 Farming. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Classes \u2013 Hidden Objects \u2013 Life &amp; Immersive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story or Setting:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the Xianxia World, almost think Survival of the Strongest, but there is one, don\u2019t want to kill, but live in peace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For powerful Beasts, he tames. For extravagant people who want to kill him, he separates their body and soul. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At the end of the whole story, he never kills, but it doesn\u2019t mean he is a good person, there is still a darkness inside.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Player Benefits:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tu Tien Path contains philosophy of Buddhism, Confucianism and Taoism, self-help, mindset of a hard worker.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Localization:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For now, just English.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Welcomes:</strong>\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discord</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Any feedbacks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Request new features.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bug report.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thank you, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Daoist Fellow!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736490218","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736490218","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/082b50fc19ced2b01619535778bf259e383b8f5d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736490218","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239330/082b50fc19ced2b01619535778bf259e383b8f5d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736490218","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Overall:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tu Tien Path is a 3D Xianxia Cultivation game, Fantasy Adventure RPG in UNREAL ENGINE 5.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are free on your own path in the world. But you will be loneliness, and very consistency i